            <body>
                <div style="text-align: center;"><font style="font-size: 24pt;"><b><u>Online Food Ordering System – System Design Document</u></b></font></div><div><br></div><div> <font style="font-size: 20pt;"><b>Introduction</b></font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">The Online Food Ordering System is a full‑stack web application designed to connect students with local food vendors. The platform allows students to browse menus, add items to a cart, place orders, and track delivery, while vendors manage food availability and orders. The system focuses on scalability, security, and smooth order workflow.</font></div><div><br></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;"><b>Tech Stack</b></font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;"><b>Frontend:</b> React.js</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;"><b>Backend:</b> Spring Boot (Java)</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;"><b>Database: </b>MySQL</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;"><b>Authentication</b>: JWT‑based authentication</font></div><div><br></div><div><font style="font-size: 20pt;"><b>System Requirements</b></font></div><div><b style="font-size: 14pt;">Functional Requirements</b></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">For Students</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Register and log in securely</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Browse food vendors and menus</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Add/remove items from cart</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Place orders</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Track order status</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">For Vendors</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Login and manage menu items</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Toggle food availability (ON/OFF)</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Accept or reject orders</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Update order status</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">For Delivery Panel</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">View assigned orders</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Update delivery status (Picked, On the Way, Delivered)</font></div><div><br></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;"><b>Non‑Functional Requirements</b></font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Secure API endpoints</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Fast response time (&lt; 2s per request)</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Scalable architecture</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Data consistency and integrity</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Role‑based access control</font></div><div><br></div><div><font style="font-size: 20pt;"><b>System Architecture Overview (High Level Design)</b></font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;"><b>Architecture Style:</b></font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Client‑Server Architecture</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">RESTful APIs</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;"><br></font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;"><b>High Level Flow:</b></font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">User interacts with React frontend</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Frontend communicates with Spring Boot backend via REST APIs</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Backend processes business logic</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Data stored and retrieved from MySQL</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">[ React Frontend ]</font></div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<font style="font-size: 14pt;"> &nbsp; |</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; v</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">[ Spring Boot REST APIs ]</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; |</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; v</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">[ MySQL Database ]</font></div><div><br></div><div><font style="font-size: 20pt;"><b>Module Breakdown (8 Modules)</b></font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;"><b style="">Frontend Modules (3)</b></font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">User Interface &amp; Authentication Module</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Menu &amp; Cart Module</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Order Tracking &amp; Delivery View Module</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;"><br></font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;"><b>Backend Modules (5)</b></font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Authentication &amp; Authorization Module</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">User &amp; Vendor Management Module</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Menu Management Module</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Order Management Module</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Delivery Management Module</font></div><div><br></div><div><font style="font-size: 20pt;"><b>Frontend Design (Low Level Design)</b></font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;"><b>Module 1: </b>User Interface &amp; Authentication (Frontend)</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Responsibilities:</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Login / Signup pages</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Role‑based dashboard (Student / Vendor / Delivery)</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Components:</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Login.jsx</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Register.jsx</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Navbar.jsx</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">ProtectedRoute.jsx</font></div><div><br></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;"><b>Module 2: </b>Menu &amp; Cart (Frontend)</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Responsibilities:</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Display vendor menus</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Add/remove items from cart</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Show total price</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Components:</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">MenuList.jsx</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">MenuItem.jsx</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Cart.jsx</font></div><div><br></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;"><b>Module 3: </b>Order Tracking &amp; Delivery View (Frontend)</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Responsibilities:</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Order status tracking</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Delivery updates</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Components:</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Orders.jsx</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">OrderDetails.jsx</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">DeliveryStatus.jsx</font></div><div><br></div><div><font style="font-size: 20pt;"><b>Backend Design (Low Level Design)</b></font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;"><b>Module 4:</b> Authentication &amp; Authorization (Backend)</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Responsibilities:</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">User login &amp; registration</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">JWT token generation</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Role‑based access</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">APIs:</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">POST /api/auth/login</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">POST /api/auth/register</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;"><br></font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;"><b>Module 5:</b> User &amp; Vendor Management (Backend)</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Responsibilities:</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Manage users and vendors</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Fetch user profiles</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">APIs:</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">GET /api/users/{id}</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">GET /api/vendors</font></div><div><br></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;"><b>Module 6: </b>Menu Management (Backend)</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Responsibilities:</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Add/update/delete menu items</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Toggle item availability</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">APIs:</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">POST /api/menu</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">PUT /api/menu/{id}/toggle</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">GET /api/menu/vendor/{vendorId}</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;"><br></font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;"><b>Module 7:</b> Order Management (Backend)</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Responsibilities:</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Create orders</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Update order status</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Manage order workflow</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Order Workflow:</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Order Placed</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Accepted by Vendor</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Preparing</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Out for Delivery</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Delivered</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">APIs:</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">POST /api/orders</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">PUT /api/orders/{id}/status</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">GET /api/orders/user/{userId}</font></div><div><br></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;"><b>Module 8: </b>Delivery Management (Backend)</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Responsibilities:</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Assign delivery personnel</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Update delivery status</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">APIs:</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">GET /api/delivery/orders</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">PUT /api/delivery/{orderId}/status</font></div><div><br></div><div><font style="font-size: 20pt;"><b>Database Design</b></font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Main Tables</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">users (id, name, email, password, role)</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">vendors (id, name, availability)</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">menu_items (id, vendor_id, name, price, available)</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">orders (id, user_id, vendor_id, status, total_price)</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">order_items (id, order_id, menu_item_id, quantity)</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">delivery (id, order_id, delivery_status)</font></div><div><br></div><div> <font style="font-size: 20pt;"><b>Security Design</b></font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">JWT‑based authentication</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Password hashing using BCrypt</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">Role‑based endpoint protection</font></div><div><font style="font-size: 14pt;">HTTPS for secure communication</font></div><div><br></div><div><font style="font-size: 20pt;"><b>Conclusion</b></font></div><p><span style="font-size: 14pt;">This system design provides a scalable, secure, and modular Online Food Ordering System suitable for student use. The clear separation of frontend and backend modules ensures maintainability and future enhancements such as payment integration or mobile app support.</span></p>
